something more groovy.

226
00:12:42,042 --> 00:12:43,342
You want groovy, baby?

227
00:12:43,342 --> 00:12:46,966
Uh-huh, I want far out,
psychedelic, groovy.

228
00:12:46,966 --> 00:12:48,509
How about Diane?

229
00:12:48,509 --> 00:12:50,071
I'm vibing Diane.

230
00:12:50,071 --> 00:12:52,657
I love diane.

231
00:12:55,835 --> 00:12:57,231
You do?

232
00:12:57,418 --> 00:12:58,691
What?

233
00:12:59,165 --> 00:13:00,850
Love me?

234
00:13:01,146 --> 00:13:02,023
I do.

235
00:13:02,023 --> 00:13:03,888
- You know what else?
- What?

236
00:13:03,888 --> 00:13:09,276
I'm gonna love ya, love ya,
love ya just a little more.

237
00:13:09,276 --> 00:13:11,139
Come here, baby.

238
00:13:15,058 --> 00:13:19,020
Joe left for work 20 minutes later...

239
00:13:19,246 --> 00:13:22,313
and I never saw him again.

240
00:13:22,924 --> 00:13:24,894
I'm sorry.

241
00:13:28,056 --> 00:13:30,454
Sometimes I think,

242
00:13:30,454 --> 00:13:34,719
My god, she'd be a woman by now.

243
00:13:35,661 --> 00:13:38,275
My little girl.

244
00:13:39,609 --> 00:13:41,201
Anyway...

245
00:13:44,035 --> 00:13:45,478
Um,

246
00:13:46,449 --> 00:13:49,391
if you think of anything else.

247
00:13:50,929 --> 00:13:52,880
Detective Rush?

248
00:13:56,007 --> 00:13:59,347
Could you tell from the tape

249
00:13:59,347 --> 00:14:05,331
